1.1.name: wordpress/udinra-all-image-sitemap
1.1.description:
Automatically creates Google XML sitemap for images and pings Google,Bing and Ask.com.

Does your website needs image sitemap at all is question in your mind then read this article

You can find list of features and comparison with other image sitemaps at Udinra Image Sitemap features

Please report bugs,feature request and other queries on this version of plugin at Support forum

You can check the difference this plugin makes to your image SEO by measuring your website performance in Google Image Search for details read this post

Pro version of this plugin is coming soon.Pro version will be complete suite for Image SEO so stay tuned.</
